title: Bench Press
description: Place plates on a bar while laying flat on your back on the bench, push straight up with the weights

title: Leg Press
description: Using the leg press machine, place your back against the bottom, and press the plate with your legs

title: Dumbbell Curls
description: With a douable weight keep your arms by yourside, and curl the weight towards your chest

title: Russian Twists
description: Twist side to side with a weight in your hands

title: Deadlift
description: Lift a bar straight up using your legs and engaging the muscles in your back

title: Calve Raises
description: Balance weight onto front of foot, push off toes to lift heels up
